<%@ Page Language="C#" AutoEventWireup="true" CodeBehind="help.aspx.cs" Inherits="Cargo.Weixin.help" %>

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head runat="server">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <title>狄乐汽服</title>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, user-scalable=no" />
    <link href="WeUI/CSS/weuix.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="WeUI/CSS/weui.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="WeUI/JS/zepto.js"></script>
    <script>
        $(function () {
            $('.collapse .js-category').click(function () {
                $parent = $(this).parent('li');
                if ($parent.hasClass('js-show')) {
                    $parent.removeClass('js-show');
                    $(this).children('i').removeClass('icon-35').addClass('icon-74');
                } else {
                    $parent.siblings().removeClass('js-show');
                    $parent.addClass('js-show');
                    $(this).children('i').removeClass('icon-74').addClass('icon-35');
                    $parent.siblings().find('i').removeClass('icon-35').addClass('icon-74');
                }
            });

        });

    </script>
</head>
<body ontouchstart class="page-bg">
    <div class="page-bd">
        <ul class="collapse">
            <li>
                <div class="weui-flex js-category">
                    <div class="weui-flex__item">怎样关注狄乐汽服微信商城</div>
                    <i class="icon icon-74"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="page-category js-categoryInner">
                    <div class="weui-cells page-category-content">
                        <p class="content">在微信----添加朋友----公众号，输入狄乐汽服，点击搜索，排位第一的即是狄乐汽服公众号，点击进入关注即可!</p>
                        <img src="wxPic/wx00.jpg" /><img src="wxPic/wx01.jpg" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="weui-flex js-category">
                    <div class="weui-flex__item">绑定商城店代码</div>
                    <i class="icon icon-74"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="page-category js-categoryInner">
                    <div class="weui-cells page-category-content">
                        <p class="content">关注狄乐汽服商城公众号后，需要联系业务员或客服，拿到属于自己的唯一店代码，输入店代码、手机号和接受到的短信验证码，所在区域，点击确定绑定按钮，绑定成功，就可以进入商城下单了!</p>
                        <img src="wxPic/wx02.jpg" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="weui-flex js-category">
                    <div class="weui-flex__item">怎样下单</div>
                    <i class="icon icon-74"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="page-category js-categoryInner">
                    <div class="weui-cells page-category-content">
                        <p class="content">绑定商城店代码后，点击《我要下单》或《轮胎商城》----《狄乐汽服特惠商城》，进入商城首页，查询商品，根据轮胎品牌和轮胎规格分类查询，找到需要的商品，点击进入商品详情页，加入购物车或立即购买操作！</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="weui-flex js-category">
                    <div class="weui-flex__item">怎样查询轮胎商品</div>
                    <i class="icon icon-74"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="page-category js-categoryInner">
                    <div class="weui-cells page-category-content">
                        <p class="content">进入商城首页，点击下方<span style="font-weight: bold; color: red;">分类</span>，在上方输入框输入轮胎规格，比如查找205/55R16规格轮胎，输入：<span style="font-weight: bold; color: red;">2055516</span>&nbsp;即可,点击输入法搜索按钮，即可出现查询结果。点击左方轮胎品牌，自动查询该品牌的2055516规格的轮胎商品显示。</p>
                        <img src="wxPic/wx03.jpg" /><img src="wxPic/wx04.jpg" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>


    </div>
      <div class="weui-footer weui-footer_fixed-bottom">
        <p class="weui-footer__text">Copyright &copy; 狄乐汽服 客服电话：<a href="tel:13265180164">13265180164</a> </p>
    </div>
